><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ide1665702625805.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ide1665702625805.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ide1665702625805\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      /aft= or /bef=\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Compile objects modified after and/or before the date specified.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ide1665702625805__p_d147755e1_d147756e1_d147757e1\">{<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/aft</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">DateTime</var>} {<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/bef</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">DateTime</var>}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1182415e76\">\n                  \n Used With\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ide1665702625805__li_d51245e1_d51246e1_d51247e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sww1665702625667.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sww1665702625667.html\" title=\"Compile all types of compilable main development objects, including components, modeled entities, and global objects.\">/all</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ide1665702625805__li_d51248e1_d51249e1_d51250e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yqf1665702625882.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yqf1665702625882.html\" title=\"Compile application shells.\">/aps or /app</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ide1665702625805__li_d51251e1_d51252e1_d51253e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"uld1665702653667.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uld1665702653667.html\" title=\"Analyze modeled entities and create entity descriptors for entities that share the same model name.\">/con (and /anm)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ide1665702625805__li_d51254e1_d51255e1_d51256e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ifp1665702626096.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ifp1665702626096.html\" title=\"Compile all components, including server pages, HTML forms, forms, reports, services, entity services, and session services.\">/cpt</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ide1665702625805__li_d51257e1_d51258e1_d51259e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wdj1665702655632.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wdj1665702655632.html\" title=\"Compile device translation tables.\">/dev</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ide1665702625805__li_d51260e1_d51261e1_d51262e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rtz1665702626248.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rtz1665702626248.html\" title=\"Compile dynamic server pages.\">/dsp</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ide1665702625805__li_d51263e1_d51264e1_d51265e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gnr1665702654145.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gnr1665702654145.html\" title=\"Compile DTD objects.\">/dtd</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ide1665702625805__li_d51266e1_d51267e1_d51268e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fvm1665702627074.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fvm1665702627074.html\" title=\"Compile Uniface form components.\">/frm</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ide1665702625805__li_d51269e1_d51270e1_d51271e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gsd1719644519908.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gsd1719644519908.html\" title=\"Compile glyphs.\">/gly</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ide1665702625805__li_d51272e1_d51273e1_d51274e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ixo1665702655853.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ixo1665702655853.html\" title=\"Compile global ProcScript and variables in a library.\">/lib</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ide1665702625805__li_d51275e1_d51276e1_d51277e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lxo1665702656136.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lxo1665702656136.html\" title=\"Compile menu bars, menus, and menu items.\">/men</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ide1665702625805__li_d51278e1_d51279e1_d51280e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ddc1665702657086.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ddc1665702657086.html\" title=\"Compile global messages, help texts, and language setups.\">/mes</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ide1665702625805__li_d51281e1_d51282e1_d51283e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tku1665702656275.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tku1665702656275.html\" title=\"Compile global objects.\">/obj</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ide1665702625805__li_d51284e1_d51285e1_d51286e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kwp1719764280859.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kwp1719764280859.html\" title=\"Compile panels.\">/pan</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ide1665702625805__li_d51287e1_d51288e1_d51289e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kjb1665702652886.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kjb1665702652886.html\" title=\"Compile Uniface report components.\">/rpt</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ide1665702625805__li_d51290e1_d51291e1_d51292e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lwo1665702653875.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lwo1665702653875.html\" title=\"Compile component signatures.\">/sig</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ide1665702625805__li_d51293e1_d51294e1_d51295e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gku1665702653234.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gku1665702653234.html\" title=\"Compile Uniface service components.\">/svc</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ide1665702625805__li_d51296e1_d51297e1_d51298e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vel1665702657161.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vel1665702657161.html\" title=\"Compile keyboard translation tables.\">/tra</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ide1665702625805__li_d51299e1_d51300e1_d51301e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"prm1665702626469.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/prm1665702626469.html\" title=\"Compile static server pages.\">/usp</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1182415e278\">\n                  \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ide1665702625805__p_d147764e1_d147765e1_d147766e1\">Use the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/aft=</span> and/or <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/bef=</span> subswitches to compile objects that have been modified after and/or before the date provided. The <var class=\"keyword varname\">DateTime</var> parameter should have the following format:</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ide1665702625805__p_d147767e1_d147768e1_d147769e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">dd</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">mm</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">yyyy</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">:</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">hh</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">:</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">nn</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">:</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ss</var>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ide1665702625805__p_d147770e1_d147771e1_d147772e1\">All the separators are optional; all the digits must be present.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528486\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528486\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "/aft= or /bef= Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 14, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 /aft= or /bef= Compile objects modified after and/or before the date specified. { /aft = DateTime } { /bef = DateTime } Used With /all /aps or /app /con (and /anm) /cpt /dev /dsp /dtd /frm /gly /lib /men /mes /obj /pan /rpt /sig /svc /tra /usp Description Use the /aft= and/or /bef= subswitches to compile objects that have been modified after and/or before the date provided. The DateTime parameter should have the following format: dd - mm - yyyy : hh : nn : ss All the separators are optional; all the digits must be present. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}